<h2>License Application</h2>
<p>The following documents, fees, and actions shall be completed and approved before a license will be issued:</p>
<hr/>

<h3>Initial Application</h3>
<ul>
	<li>A <a title="license application form" href="http://www.dshs.state.tx.us/WorkArea/linkit.aspx?LinkIdentifier=id&amp;ItemID=8589982710">license application form</a> <span class="small">(PDF, 175KB)</span> shall be submitted no earlier than 90 calendar days prior to the projected opening date of the facility.</li>
	<li>A license fee of $5,000.00 shall be submitted. <em>License fees are not refundable.</em></li>
	<li>The applicant or the applicant’s representative shall attend a pre-survey conference at the zone office designated by the department. Please <a title="contact the designated zone office" href="/facilities/compliance-contact.aspx">contact the designated zone office</a> to schedule the pre-survey conference.</li>
</ul>	
<hr/>

<h3>Change of Ownership (CHOW) Application</h3>
<ul>
	<li>A <a title="license application form" href="http://www.dshs.state.tx.us/WorkArea/linkit.aspx?LinkIdentifier=id&amp;ItemID=8589982710">license application form</a> <span class="small">(PDF, 175KB)</span> shall be be submitted at least 60 calendar days before the date of the change of ownership.</li>
	<li>A license fee of $5,000.00 shall be submitted. <em>License fees are not refundable.</em></li>
	<li>The applicant or the applicant’s representative shall attend a pre-survey conference at the zone office designated by the department. The designated zone office may waive the pre-survey conference requirement for a Change of Ownership. Please <a title="contact the designated zone office" href="/facilities/compliance-contact.aspx">contact the designated zone office</a> to schedule the pre-survey conference or to request a wavier.</li>
	<li>The applicant shall include evidence (bill of sale, lease agreement, or legal court document) of the change of ownership. This document can be submitted separately from the license application.</li>
</ul>	
<hr/>

<h2>Survey Components </h2>
<p>During the initial licensing period, department zone office staff will conduct an on-site survey to ascertain compliance with the provisions of the <a title="Health and Safety Code and associated rules" href="/facilities/abortion/laws-rules.aspx">Health and Safety Code and associated rules</a>. An entrance conference will be held with key facility personnel. Zone office staff will explain the survey process and answer questions. During the survey, zone office staff will:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Review clinical records</li>
    <li>Review facility policies and procedures</li>
    <li>Review quality assurance activities</li>
    <li>Review personnel records</li>
    <li>Interview staff</li>
    <li>Conduct an exit conference with key facility personnel</li>
    <li>Discuss survey findings.</li>
</ul>
<hr/>

